NAME
    Cache::LRU::WithExpires - can set an expiration for the Cache::LRU

SYNOPSIS
      use Cache::LRU::WithExpires;

      my $cache = Cache::LRU::WithExpires->new;
      $cache->set('foo', 'bar', 1);
      sleep 2;
      $cache->get('foo'); # undef

DESCRIPTION
    Cache::LRU::WithExpires is a can set an expiration for the Cache::LRU.

